  <brief_title>Effect of Toothpaste Fortified With Cyanocobalamin on Vitamin B12 Status</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Toothpaste Fortified With Cyanocobalamin on Vitamin B12 Status: A 3 Month Placebo Controlled Randomized Study</official_title>
