  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adults: men and women

          -  Stable diet for at least 24 months (omnivorous or a vegan diet).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnancy and lactation

          -  Malabsorption disorders (Crohn disease, chronic gastritis, pernicious anemia, gastric
             or intestinal resection)

          -  Renal diseases

          -  Liver diseases

          -  Patients with cancer (or cancer history)

          -  Pre-study treatment with vitamin B12 or folate
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
